nodes.text: Manaan sliders were one of the speciality sliders on the menu at Dex's Diner on the planet Coruscant. It was inspired by the water world Manaan and consisted of a Firaxan shark fillet, in place of the standard Mongo Beefhead patty, topped with Ahto City cheese, chewy Selkathian seaweed and relish squiggles served on a trans-shipped medium-density food-board. It cost 6.7 credits.
